item.title: Now
item.description: September 2022 ∘ Learning C with "Learning C for Pebble". ∘ Started and finished a complete redesign of the website to it's final form. ∘ Still working on an accessible version of my iPod theme for people with vision difficulties. ∘ Began writing a technical book for writing rockbox themes for ipods. ∘ Starting taking some photos again. What’s Playing? ∘ Currently Reading Yu Yu Hakusho. ∘ Listening to Black Focus by Yussef Kamaal.
